4.77/5  rDev +3.5%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.5A - Clear brown port colored with ruby highlights that glimmer in the glass. A creamy white pillow of head that laces the glass but dissipates rather quickly. Thin appearance on the pour. 
