4.97/5  rDev +7.8%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5Had this at "In de Vrede" cafe near the Sint-Sixtus Abdij in Vleteren, Belgium, after taking a 2-hour train ride from Brussels to Ieper and biking for 20 km. 
